Oracle Consultant Stuff
Confidential Company -
Date Posted: 2014/05/03 12:54:36
Ref. JB3046768
Job Description
Oracle Consultant Team :
- Oracle Financial Consultant
(Job Ref:FMS)
- Oracle Supply Chain Consultant
(Job Ref:SCM)
- Oracle HR Consultant
(Job Ref:HCM)
- Oracle Project Consultant
(Job Ref:OPC)
- Oracle Apps Developer
(Job Ref:DEV)
- Oracle Apps DBA
(Job Ref:DBA)
- Oracle Manufactering Consultant
(Job Ref:OMC)
- Oracle Implementation Project Manager
(Job Ref:OPM)
Skills
Oracle Supply Chain Consultant Skills
Education/Qualifications/Experience
• Experience of implementations using a structured methodology such as AIM or Prince2
Distribution)
At least Four years of experience on Oracle Distribution (Oracle
Purchasing, Inventory, Order Management and Advanced Pricing)
Implementations to have been done in Distribution or retail companies
Preference to have implemented in Saudi Arabia.
-experience in Oracle Applications in supply chain/logistics modules
least 2 Full Implementation Cycles in at least 3 modules of Oracle Distribution & Logistics modules(Inventory, Purchasing, Order Management, iProcurement, ...).
Using AIM methodology and its documents with understanding of Oracle ERP projects life-cycle.
business communication skills in both Arabic and English languages, including professional business writing.
team player with excellent communication, interpersonal and presentation skills
_____________________________________________
Oracle HR Consultant Skills :
- At least 2 Full Implementation Cycles in at least 4 modules of Oracle HRMS modules (HR Core, Payroll, SSHR, iRecruitment, OTL, OLM).
- AIM professional creator/designer, using Visio as well.
- Having expertise in projects documentation, and having his/her own templates library.
- Native business communication skills in both Arabic and English languages, including professional business
writing, conducting meetings, customer relationships …Etc.
- Advanced Study(ies)/ prfoessional certificate(s) in Human Resources is a plus, or equal business experience.
- Project Management skills and its correlated tools (MS Project, Visio, AIM and Office Package).
- Assertive presentation and persuasive skills, facilitation skills and figurehead.
- Team Leading, proactive, self-learning, positive attitude, eager to development and growth, presentable, having -
team spirit and knowledge-sharing attitude.
- Task-oriented.
- Software development background.
- Distinctive analytical skills.
- Preffered to be Implemented in manufacturing companies or similar industries.
- Communication & presentation skills.
- Problem solving skills.
______________________________________________
Oracle Financial Consultant Skills :
- Experience in General Accounting, Accounts Receivable, Accounts Payable, Cash Management, Fixed Assets & Consolidation. Job Cost, Project Costing.
- Implementation and support on Oracle Financial 12 & 11
- Should have implemented, witnessed and participated in three to four full Oracle Financials implementation (GL, AP, AR, Cash management, Fixed Assets)
Could be a team member in two implementations, but should be a team leader in at least two implementations.
- Experience in Business Process Optimization, Improvement or Re-engineering.
- Should be willing to contribute his experiences with project management office
- Understanding implicit requirements in functional specifications and making a thorough content validation.
- Strong organizational, multi-tasking, and time-management skills.
- Professional demeanor and presence a must!
- Complete functional designs and review technical designs for custom reports, interfaces or extensions impacting the financials area.
- Complete Start to Finish Implementations, Process Redesign, and Issue.
- Distinctive analytical skills.
- Preffered to be Implemented in manufacturing,Retail,Contracting companies
- Communication & presentation skills.
- Problem solving skills.
________________________________________________
Who We Are:
we are a leading IT Company located in Egypt, 6 October
subsidiary of Gulf Holding Group.
To apply:
